- content_for :title, "Eligibility Reviews - Coming Soon"

= render 'shared/coming_soon_hero', feature_name: 'Eligibility Reviews'

.card
  .card-header
    %h4.mb-0
      %i.bi.bi-clipboard-check.me-2
      Eligibility Review System
  .card-body
    .row
      .col-md-8
        %h5 What are Eligibility Reviews?
        %p Eligibility reviews help answer "What do I need to demonstrate to show eligibility for a new ability milestone, a new Assignment, or ultimately a new Position?"
        
        %h6.mt-4 Review Types:
        %ul
          %li
            %strong Ability Milestone Eligibility: 
            %span.text-muted What milestones are needed for the next ability level?
          %li
            %strong Assignment Eligibility: 
            %span.text-muted What abilities and experience are required for new assignments?
          %li
            %strong Position Eligibility: 
            %span.text-muted What's needed to qualify for a new position?
        
        %h6.mt-4 Key Features:
        %ul
          %li Gap analysis between current state and requirements
          %li Development planning based on eligibility gaps
          %li Progress tracking toward eligibility requirements
          %li Clear pathways for career advancement
        
        %h6.mt-4 Vision:
        %p This system will provide the growth and development framework that enables employees to continuously improve their accountability and capabilities.
        
      .col-md-4
        .card.bg-light
          .card-body
            %h6.text-primary
              %i.bi.bi-graph-up.me-2
              Career Growth
            %p.small Clear pathways for career advancement and skill development.
            
            %hr
            
            %h6.text-success
              %i.bi.bi-check-circle.me-2
              Clear Requirements
            %ul.small
              %li Gap identification
              %li Development planning
              %li Progress tracking
              %li Achievement recognition
